t any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Clerk requirements High School diploma or equivalent Excellent keyboarding skills, with 95% accuracy or higher High level communication skills and a positive attitude Ability to work with minimal supervision Strong organizational and time management skills Previous experience in a customer facing role is strongly preferred Clerk related job titles: Jury Clerk Data Entry Clerk Intake Clerk Communications Clerk Ward Clerk Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
